10#include <openssl/camellia.h>
11#include "cmll_locl.h"
12
13void Camellia_ecb_encrypt(const unsigned char *in, unsigned char *out,
14 const CAMELLIA_KEY *key, const int enc)
15{
16 if (CAMELLIA_ENCRYPT == enc)
17 Camellia_encrypt(in, out, key);
18 else
19 Camellia_decrypt(in, out, key);
20}
